  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM2.2.2">
<l>ēpā vampara mēyē ḻulaku</l>
<l>mīpā vañcey taruḷā laḷippārār</l>
<l>māpā vamviṭa varaṟkup piccaipey</l>
<l>kōpāla kōḷari yēṟaṉṟiyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>What sins are paramount in the seven worlds,</l>
<l>who will by grace make these sins [vanish  and] take care,</l>
<l>if not the cow-herding bull of a murderous lion</l>
<l>who poured alms for Hara so that [his] great sin left?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
